Library to print Invitation label

Input -
    A list of record (as File)
    format -
        firstName,lastName,Honorific,age,city,state,country

Requirement -
    filter according to age
    provide vouchers to person above age 20

Output -
    +---------------+
    | Mr First Last |
    |---------------|
    | city, state   |
    | country       |
    +---------------+
        or
    +----------------+
    | Mr Last, First |
    |----------------|
    | city, state    |
    | country        |
    +----------------+

Prefix -
    Male as Mr
    Female as Ms

=============================================================

